<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mock Content Page for RAG Chatbot</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 2em; }
        .personal-info, .section { background: #f5f5f5; padding: 1em; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 2em; }
        h2 { color: #764ba2; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Mock Content for RAG Chatbot</h1>
    <div class="personal-info">
        <h2>Personal Information</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Name:</strong> Huayu</li>
            <li><strong>Birth Date:</strong> March 12th, 1989</li>
            <li><strong>Age:</strong> 36</li>
            <li><strong>Zodiac Sign:</strong> Pisces</li>
            <li><strong>Chinese Zodiac:</strong> Snake</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <h2>Professional Experience</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>2022–Present:</strong> Senior Software Engineer at TechNova</li>
            <li><strong>2018–2022:</strong> Full Stack Developer at WebWorks</li>
            <li><strong>2015–2018:</strong> Junior Developer at CodeCrafters</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <h2>Education</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>MSc Computer Science</strong>, University of Example, 2015</li>
            <li><strong>BSc Information Technology</strong>, Example State University, 2013</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <h2>Favorite Books</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>"Sapiens: A Brief History of Humankind" by Yuval Noah Harari</li>
            <li>"The Pragmatic Programmer" by Andrew Hunt and David Thomas</li>
            <li>"The Three-Body Problem" by Liu Cixin</li>
            <li>"Atomic Habits" by James Clear</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <h2>World Capitals</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>France: Paris</li>
            <li>Japan: Tokyo</li>
            <li>Brazil: Brasília</li>
            <li>Canada: Ottawa</li>
            <li>Australia: Canberra</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <h2>Science Facts</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>The speed of light is approximately 299,792 kilometers per second.</li>
            <li>Water is composed of two hydrogen atoms and one oxygen atom (H<sub>2</sub>O).</li>
            <li>Honey never spoils and can last thousands of years.</li>
            <li>Bananas are berries, but strawberries are not.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <dl>
            <dt>What is RAG?</dt>
            <dd>Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) is an AI technique that combines retrieval of relevant documents with generative models to provide more accurate and grounded responses.</dd>
            <dt>How do I use this chatbot?</dt>
            <dd>Type your question in the chat window. The chatbot will use the content on this page and its backend knowledge to answer.</dd>
            <dt>Can I ingest new content?</dt>
            <dd>Yes, if enabled, you can ingest new content for the chatbot to use in its responses.</dd>
        </dl>
    </div>
    <div id="chatbot-container"></div>
    <!-- Use Python backend RAG service -->
    <script type="module" src="chatbot_python.js"></script>
    <script>
        // Wait for DOM to be fully loaded
        if (document.readyState === 'loading') {
            document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', initializeChatbot);
        } else {
            initializeChatbot();
        }
        function initializeChatbot() {
            setTimeout(() => {
                initRAGChatbot({
                    selector: '#chatbot-container',
                    theme: { primaryColor: '#764ba2' },
                    welcomeMessage: 'Hi! Ask me about Huayu, world capitals, superheroes, pizza, science, or anything else!',
                    enableContentIngestion: true,
                    enableRAG: true,
                    backendUrl: 'http://localhost:8001'
                });
            }, 100);
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html> 